Message format

Worldview
includes
	state						{init, moving, idle, doors_open, emergency}
	last_floor					{1, 2, 3, 4}
	dir							{UP, DOWN, STOP}
	ID 							{_}
	local_orders 				{1, 2, 3, 4}
	#%//(destination)//
format
	tuple


Hall Order
includes
	floor 						{1, 2, 3, 4}
	dir							{UP, DOWN}
